From: Stefan Agner <stefan.agner@toradex.com>
Date: Thu, 19 Sep 2019 16:48:39 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] colibri_imx7: add addresses required for distro boot

Define addresses required for full distro boot support.

Signed-off-by: Stefan Agner <stefan.agner@toradex.com>
---
 include/configs/colibri_imx7.h | 4 +++-
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/include/configs/colibri_imx7.h b/include/configs/colibri_imx7.h
index 5c19fa0e84..52f8d5afbf 100644
--- a/include/configs/colibri_imx7.h
+++ b/include/configs/colibri_imx7.h
@@ -70,7 +70,9 @@
 	"fdt_high=0xffffffff\0" \
 	"initrd_high=0xffffffff\0" \
 	"kernel_addr_r=0x81000000\0" \
-	"ramdisk_addr_r=0x82100000\0"
+	"pxefile_addr_r=0x87100000\0" \
+	"ramdisk_addr_r=0x82100000\0" \
+	"scriptaddr=0x87000000\0"
 
 #if defined(CONFIG_TARGET_COLIBRI_IMX7_NAND)
 #define SD_BOOTDEV 0
